2. The 31st day of July 2021 is appointed as the day on which the Sale of 
Tickets (Cultural, Entertainment, Recreational and Sporting Events) Act 2021 
(No. 21 of 2021) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

28 July, 2021. 

LEO VARADKAR, 

Minister for Enterprise, Trade and Employment.. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 30th July, 2021.
